game
Provided game package, containing all packages used to implement the game.
game.actions
Contains all action classes specialized for the game.
game.actions.consumption
Contains all consumption actions for consumable items related classes specialized for the game.
game.actions.pickups
Contains all pick-up/re-fill/stocking action related classes specialized for the game.
game.actions.speech
Contains all speaking related classes specialized for the game.
game.actors
Contains all actor classes specialized for the game.
game.actors.allies
Contains all ally related classes specialized for the game.
game.actors.enemies
Contains all enemy related classes specialized for the game.
game.behaviours
Contains all behaviours (currently only used by enemies) for the game.
game.grounds
Contains all ground classes for the game.
game.grounds.fountains
Contains all fountain ground types
game.grounds.trees
Contains all tree classes (a subclass of the grounds) for the game.
game.items
Contains all item classes required for the itemization in game.
game.items.consumable
Contains all items that are consumable
game.items.permanent
Contains all items that are non-consumable
game.reset
Contains all classes required to do the reset (Requirement 7)
game.utilities
Contains all extra classes used only for utility to make the code cleaner.
